    "name": "Peregrino",
    "steam_appid": 3268150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《朝圣者》是一款等距视角的生存与管理游戏，你将带领一群朝圣者穿越一片被诅咒的土地，在通往乐土的旅途中做出生死抉择。<br><br>踏入这片阴森的中间之地，证明你的信仰，幸存于守护它的亵渎怪物之间，并通过艰难的选择引导你的追随者走向命运……也影响你自身的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/566019e15f024b14f1c99019f0eaf65d.poster.avif?t=1772490323\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/566019e15f024b14f1c99019f0eaf65d.webm?t=1772490323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>残酷的生存管理</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片无情的土地上收集、狩猎与战斗以求生存。管理稀缺资源，保证朝圣者吃饱睡稳，并为黄昏做好准备——那时新伊甸的神圣守卫将展开狩猎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/5e8e9bef66c308596528fd11a2f47aee.poster.avif?t=1772490323\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/5e8e9bef66c308596528fd11a2f47aee.webm?t=1772490323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>毛骨悚然的恐怖之旅</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对可怖、亵渎、梦魇般的怪物——那些考验你是否配得上的神圣守卫。战斗不足以救你，唯有信仰才是试炼的关键。这些怪物在夜晚变得更强，但能坚持下去的，也将获得更丰厚的回报。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/a15cba4b2d7fb70565238ca78266ee42.poster.avif?t=1772490323\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/a15cba4b2d7fb70565238ca78266ee42.webm?t=1772490323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>以角色为核心的无情旅程</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不仅带领一支商队，你还肩负着生命。每位朝圣者都有独特的故事、技能与前往新伊甸的理由。管理他们的需求与士气，但请记住：死亡是永久的，你的决定将影响他们是否愿意继续前行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/d69be5bc50cb2f81bc1dd212a3623649.poster.avif?t=1772490323\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/d69be5bc50cb2f81bc1dd212a3623649.webm?t=1772490323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>信仰的堡垒</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的商队是你的家、你的希望，也是抵御黑暗的唯一屏障。升级并自定义你的车队，加固防御，扩展储物空间，提升机动性……为即将到来的挑战做好准备。越深入，旅途越残酷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/a406fe3e760ade1c6246f6982fb28765.poster.avif?t=1772490323\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/a406fe3e760ade1c6246f6982fb28765.webm?t=1772490323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>风险、回报与工艺</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谨慎选择你在森林中的路径，管理好你的物品栏，在为时已晚之前带着战利品撤离。资源稀缺，空间有限。决定该带什么、该舍弃什么，以及如何将残骸转化为关键的工具、武器和补给。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/30125caf7915aaa8ae84fc231d1e6ef0.poster.avif?t=1772490323\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268150/extras/30125caf7915aaa8ae84fc231d1e6ef0.webm?t=1772490323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>19世纪的阴郁幻景</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于一个受哥特式恐怖与宗教传说启发的阴森世界，展现出19世纪的手工风格与黑暗美学。每次游玩都是独一无二的——由你遇见的人、面对的恐惧与做出的抉择共同塑造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
